text: Hönig or Hoenig is a German surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Ari Hoenig (born 1973), jazz drummer, composer and educator *Eugen Honig (1873–1945) *Franz-Josef Hönig (born 1942), German footballer *Heinz Hoenig, German actor *Jonathan Hoenig (born 1975), managing member at Capitalist Pig hedge fund *Michael Hoenig (born 1952), German composer *Ron Hoenig, Australian Barrister at Law, politician *Sebastian F. Hönig, DFG fellow in the astrophysics group of the University of California *Thomas M. Hoenig (born 1946) eighth chief executive of the Tenth District Federal Reserve Bank, in Kansas City, United States. *Wolfgang Hönig (born 1954), German rower ==See also== *51983 Hönig, a main belt asteroid *Hoenig v Isaacs Category:German- language surnames (VANESSA ROSSE MARIE ACOSTA HÖNIG) {18/NOV/2000}
